{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Decimate endless hordes of enemies across the nine realms of Yggdrasil for eternal glory! Plains of Havoc is a fierce 2D top-down roguelite set in the Viking afterlife in which you fight for your rightful place on the global leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212550/extras/Slaughter_Endless_Waves_1.2.png?t=1730183761\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212550/extras/steam_gif1.gif?t=1730183761\" />Fight against endless hordes of monsters in the Viking afterlife, Valhalla! There are unlimited waves to survive against, but they each grow stronger than the last - the faster you defeat them the faster you'll level up. Survive for as long as you can until the wave overwhelms you in glorious death!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212550/extras/Tons_Of_Upgrades_1.2.png?t=1730183761\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2212550/extras/steam_gif2.gif?t=1730183761\" />Choose from a range of upgrades during each run to match your playstyle! Zap your enemies with chain lightning, blow up their corpses to spread fire or go all out berserker and shred your way through the horde! Become even more powerful when you meet your inevitable demise through permanent upgrades, transcending the gods themselves!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Better than my Mum","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2212550/1703e77bd9421fb1488e6c922cc0569d4d0f6463.jpg"},{"name":"Just one more run","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2212550/1703e77bd9421fb1488e6c922c